Known Linux/Win32 bugs:

1) Crash occurs when a / is missing from a URL. This crashes, http://example.com while this works: http://example.com/

Known NDS bugs:
The NDS version has the bugs from the Linux/Win32 versions, as well as:

1) CyaSSL doesn't even try connecting to server, CyaSSL port compiling issue perhaps?

Known Wii bugs:
The Wii version has the bugs from the Linux/Win32 versions, as well as:

1) Networking doesn't work. net_socket returns -123, net_connect returns -81. Both are unknown errors.

